content: Purchased application for $1.99 and it won't even open. Have tried uninstalling and reinstalling with no luck.
replyContent: Sorry for the trouble! We just release an update that should fix this issue for your device. Please contact support@thup.com if you have any issues in the future, and apologies again!

content: I already paid a few years ago. I have to pay again??
replyContent: We do not have any control over how apps are paid for, that is all handled by Google Play. However, they always let you download again as long as you are on the same Google account. Check your account or contact Google Support.

content: My son loves the game but no matter where I download the app it has no sound can you guys please fix this?!!
replyContent: Sorry for the trouble! We released an update that had a sound issue on some devices.  This has been fixed and a new update was released yesterday.  Please contact us if you have any other problems.

The hardest part is for the parent to not jump in and show the child how to do it because they will have a small struggle at first which is good.  My only recommendation is for the games to get harder faster so it remains a challenge.
